Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124736,1127614}We can talk just fine here in the car,\Nso where are you taking me?{NOTE:話なら車の中だってできるのに。どうして？}
