Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:26.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165861,1166737}Slow down.{NOTE:待ってったら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175120,1176121}Miki-san.{NOTE:美紀さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179041,1180459}What did you want to talk…{NOTE:お話があるなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185839,1187257}Who are these people?{NOTE:何なのこの人達？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187257,1188133}You know them?{NOTE:お知り合い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:48.80,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188133,1188800}Who knows?{NOTE:さあ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189843,1193221}I don't know what's going on but this is pretty underhanded.{NOTE:どう言うことが知らないけど、随分卑怯な手を使うよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.26,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194056,1195265}Underhanded?{NOTE:卑怯？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.68,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195265,1197684}You've got some nerve saying that!{NOTE:白々しく、よくもそんなこと言えるわね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.73,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199186,1202731}Since you're playing dumb, I'll be frank.{NOTE:言えないなら、私からこの際はっきりと言ってあげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:06.02,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202731,1206026}Unless you're stupid, you should remember this little present you just gave me.{NOTE:馬鹿じゃない限り、自分のプレゼントしたもの忘れはしないわよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.44,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208820,1211448}A handkerchief suits you well.{NOTE:ハンカチなんて、あなたらしいプレゼントね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.24,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214910,1217245}Girls should be honest.{NOTE:女の子は素直な方がいいです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.12,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217245,1219122}It was from you, wasn't it?{NOTE:やっぱりあなただったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.20,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219664,1221208}That's fine.{NOTE:それならそれでいいけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.62,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221208,1224628}I just want you to explain to me,\Nwhat these initials mean?{NOTE:意味ありげなイニシャルを入れたり、一体何の意味なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225212,1226880}I don't even know what you're talking about.{NOTE:勝手な事ばかりなんて言わないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.96,Default,Kouda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228131,1230967}I get angry when people try to keep things from me.{NOTE:私はね、他人に隠し事されると腹が立つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230967,1231968}What the heck?{NOTE:何のこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:52.61,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251321,1252614}Wait, you hussy!{NOTE:このやろ、待て！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.57,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252614,1253573}Get back here!{NOTE:待てよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.79,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260997,1262791}Now, tell the lady what she wants.{NOTE:さ、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.96,Default,Henchman B,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262791,1264960}It's better for you that way.{NOTE:その方が好きにするぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.25,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268630,1270257}What… what's that?{NOTE:な、何だあれは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.92,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272926,1273927}It's Nozomi!{NOTE:のぞみだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.51,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273927,1275512}Damn. Hold tight.{NOTE:しくしょ。捕まってろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.55,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275512,1276555}Wait what?!{NOTE:何だ何だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.34,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276555,1278348}Whatcha gonna do?{NOTE:俺たち何やってるんだ？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.93,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280016,1280934}Hey, tough guy!{NOTE:このやろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280934,1282269}– Hotta-kun!\N– Company!{NOTE:—堀田くん。\\N—こいつ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.81,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282269,1283812}Damn! Get them!{NOTE:くそ！やっちまえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.43,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283812,1285438}All right! You're on, you piece of trash!{NOTE:よし！やろう、このやろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.44,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288817,1290443}Take this! And this! And this!{NOTE:この！この！この！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.28,Default,Henchman A,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293363,1295282}Crap! Let's run!{NOTE:XX逃げろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:41.99,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301246,1301997}Get lost!{NOTE:消えちまえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.62,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301997,1303623}And don't ever come back!{NOTE:XXXやろうぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.87,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304791,1306877}What scumbags.{NOTE:何て胸糞も悪いやつらなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308420,1309629}Thank you, Hotta-kun.{NOTE:有難う。堀田くん。}
