Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312382,1313258}Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.30,Default,Unknown blonde guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313258,1315302}D-Did he kiss you or anything?{NOTE:き、キスなんか流されなかったか？}
